stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Drafted

    Drafted --> Validated: technical validation passed
    Validated --> Approved: governance approval granted
    Approved --> Deployed: release action executed
    Deployed --> Monitored: production checks healthy

    Monitored --> RolledBack: incident / drift / failure
    RolledBack --> Monitored: stable previous version restored

    Monitored --> Retired: planned retirement
    Approved --> Retired: cancelled before deployment

    Retired --> [*]
